At last night's match we honored the life of Ben Cowherd, who passed away last week.

Ben was the beat of The Backline, always drumming his heart away with a welcoming smile and spirit that were greater than life. Soccer was his tool to care and stand up for those in need, and with that he built a community of soccer fans and friends whose backgrounds surpassed borders.

The legacy continues 🎙️
 
On the 52nd anniversary of Johnny Cash’s Man in Black album release, we’re proud to present the Man in Black Collector's Box. Created in partnership with the Estate of Johnny Cash, the Collector’s Box celebrates the life and legacy of the Man in Black. Only 1,000 Collector's Boxes are available worldwide at nashvillesc.com/boxset.
 
The Collector's Box includes:
 
▪️ An LED screen of a Johnny Cash image
▪️ A Man in Black Hatch Show Print
▪️ An authentic Man in Black jersey with a unique moniker on the back
▪️ Four custom designed metal guitar picks
▪️ A metal display all-access pass
▪️ A custom Nashville SC x Johnny Cash guitar strap
